    "7321941": {
        "Desc": "Go deeper into the temple",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, why did you stop us? The thing we're looking for is just up ahead..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Shh!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why did we stop?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Look behind you — we're not alone."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7321909": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Azariq",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "The temple's safe. I don't see any enemies, monsters, or dangerous devices."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "There's just this big thing... Heh. How interesting."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "According to archaeological records left by people who came before us, as well as a stone slate that Aderfi got from within some ruins..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "This big object over here is the main device that keeps the Mother of the Jinn sealed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Just from basic observation, I'd say that it's connected to the machine next to it. Perhaps they can be made to move in tandem somehow."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh... So we'll need to unlock this one by the side here to move the big object in the middle...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "That's about right, I think. As for what happens afterward... I think we'll just have to cross that river when we get there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Funny, I don't see any rivers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Oh, knock it off, Jeht."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "So, I think we just need to repeat what we did at the gate... Let's crack this device open, shall we?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7321910": {
        "Desc": "Activate the device within the temple",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Hello... Guest of Tanit..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "J—J—Jeht mentions you often. She's a good kid."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are you up to?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Planting crops and f—feeding the fish. Sometimes, I also do some b—b—butchery. Crocodile skin and meat is v—very useful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Crocodiles, you say!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Hehe, yes. I—I take care of them. These are quite large and obedient..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "This one's c—c—called Sedim. Very fierce and strong, and skin's very vibrant. It'll make for a good satchel. And there's that one, Karam. It's small but plump. Rather gentle, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "We get clean spring water all year around h—here, so it's just right for raising crocodiles. Th—that's why we fenced this place up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Crocodiles are easy to care for, and they can be harvested for lots of skins and meat. Unfortunately, f—fields are a d—different story..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You have fields around here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "We do... but only for testing. Matriarch Babel invited some outsiders to c—c—come and provide us with Anahitian Blessing, and she got all these old books from the city..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "S—s—so we've tried our hand at farming according to the contents of these books."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "But the oases in the canyon are too narrow and lack nutrients. We need to find a way to f—fertilize the soil."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Tell me about the Anahitian Blessing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "The outsiders didn't want to reveal the fertilizer's composition. As such, we've had to rely on the people who provide it to f—fertilize the soil... which isn't good."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Th—that's why the Matriarch wants me to d—do some research here to r—reverse engineer our own Anahitian Blessing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I shan't disturb you any longer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Th—that's alright. Please take some crocodile jerky, dear guest. It's just over there..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7321962": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7321911": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Azariq",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Well, the machine has started, and the sand pile is gone... But the main device hasn't responded at all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Did it not work?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "#Wait, {NICKNAME}. You're the only one here who can use the elements, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Hmm...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Well, what I mean to say is that unlike us, who need to borrow the power of ancient spirits, your elemental abilities are innate, yes?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Yeah, that is the case."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So, what about it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Why don't you try touching this big thing over here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Um... But... What if it turns out to be super dangerous?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't worry about it, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We've touched all kinds of crazy things in the past, Paimon..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You say that... But we should be careful all the same!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
