    "7321961": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Is the conversation with Matriarch Babel over?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "In that case... Let's take a short break."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7321913": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Azariq",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Hah, that's what I thought... Looks like the device earlier smoothed out its charging... uh, circuits? Looks like it's showing us the location of three other devices, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "I suppose that if we go to these devices, we'll be able to activate all four of these seal-breaking machines and clear the sand piles in front of us..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Aye, I think that's how it is... judging from my previous ruin-delving experiences, anyway."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow! You sure do know a lot... and here Paimon thought you were just some guy in a tribe somewhere..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Hey, hey, give the man some respect, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? Oh! ... Sorry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Hahaha, what do you even mean by that, Paimon? I'm a tribeswoman myself!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Alright, alright. Enough chit-chat. Let's follow the directions we've been given and look for the other three devices."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Hmm... Let me think. Let's start here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "How do you know that we need to go this way first?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Haha. A desert dweller's intuition, perhaps?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Hmph... If we get lost, it's on your head!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Relax. Both of us are here. If things go bad, we can fight our way out... or flee to safety."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7321914": {
        "Desc": "Open the gate",
        "Tips": "Attack the Rune Mechanism and ablate the sand pile",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Masseira",
                    "T": "Spoken to Babel, have you? Ah, she's probably busying herself somewhere else again... You would sooner stop the wind than stop her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Masseira",
                    "T": "Haha... You know, youngster, speaking of the wind... I'd like to remind you of a kind of desert wind that we call \"Zibri.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Masseira",
                    "T": "At first, you won't sense anything, until the sandstorm rises over the horizon, and the air itself begins to ascend and burn. Only then will you realize..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Masseira",
                    "T": "...That you can no longer smell anything, for the heated air has smothered your sense of smell, seared your nostrils..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Masseira",
                    "T": "By then... Heh. By then, it will be too late."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm afraid I didn't catch your drift..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Masseira",
                    "T": "It's nothing... I just mean to say that you should be careful of the sandstorms."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
