    "7321933": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Azariq",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Have a look at this!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The sand retreated..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So this was beneath the desert all the while..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "That's right. More ruins!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "A plaza with sides of seemingly equal length... and a new door's opened up on the opposite cliff. Is that our destination?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "That's for you to explore, I fear."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Eh? Aren't you coming with us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Sorry, but Matriarch Babel only asked me to open the way for you. You'll have to embark on the rest of the road yourself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "I trust that you can protect your friends, right, Jeht?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Oh, stop with that, you. What are you, my dad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I know... Stay safe while you're heading back, you hear me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "#Of course. {NICKNAME}, you take care of Jeht as well!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh. Why's Azariq just up and leaving on us like that? Isn't he gonna go deeper into the ruins with us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "He's gone as deep as he wants to go, I think. These ruins are a cursed, taboo place to us Tanit... and the tribe's quite sensitive about that sort of thing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "But since I count as \"half-outsider,\" I've got no qualms about going further. And anyway, you can't expect me to let you guys down!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And you did ask us to help you find this Oasis thingamajiggie anyway, right? We're with you to the end!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Haha, thanks!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, let's proceed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We've only got each other from here on out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Yup. Don't worry, I'll watch your back for sure!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
