    "7318607": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Jeht",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "This is a Tanit camp... It even has the tribe's markings."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Matriarch Babel must've sent someone here ahead of us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Oh, ho? What's this? Someone appears to be less attuned to the traditions they so claim to practice than they'd like..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is there something wrong with the campsite?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh... What's wrong with the campsite? Paimon's not seeing anything here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "She dispatched people to comb this area before our arrival. However, I perceive that they never made it out. Perhaps it is because of such that this place was marked as \"forbidden.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Which means that this area was forbidden for matters of practicality, and not terrors wrought of superstition."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "As for why she sent people here with regularity prior... It could not just be to sate the desire of young Jeht here... More camps lie ahead, I would warrant."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...We'll ask Matriarch Babel about this once we get back. For now, we keep moving."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
