    "7318610": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Liloupar",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "What... What is this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Though I really don't want to act without thinking things through, I have a feeling that if we want to continue, we'll need to activate this thing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm, but what if it's dangerous?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "This is a water-pumping mechanism. It was used to attune to the flow and vectors of water... Though now, water's place in its pipes has been usurped by sand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "*sigh* As surely as you are witness, this once was a lush garden, in a time when the flowing springs had yet to become a fleeting rarity amongst the sands."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Enough talk. I think I may yet be able to spark function back into this mechanism... Allow me to try, my master."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#It sure sounds like this place is familiar to Liloupar. {NICKNAME}, let's just let her give it a go!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
