    "7318617": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Liloupar",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "As the shard of light merges with Liloupar's magic bottle, you feel a little of your own power being pulled away..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Through the Jinni's entranced eyes, you see a ragged shepherd boy along with a dancing maiden, her presence resplendent like a limpid gem beneath the moon's gaze...\\nFestering hatred assails your senses, before alchemizing into primal, burning love in a sudden instant...\\nSuch love cannot be contained by the vessel of a mortal. It is an emotion that can swallow one whole."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "\"Then, mortal... What desire of yours can I make manifest?\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}! Are you alright? Answer me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}! Don't scare Paimon like that! Are you okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Worry not... my master remains unscathed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sorry, I was out of it for a moment..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#{M#\"Out of it?\" I thought you lost consciousness!}{F#Really? I thought you were seized by something foul within the bottle!}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! You worried Paimon sick!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It was a memory. Someone else's memory..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Huh? I don't... What are you saying?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Apologies. I did not mean to let you behold a moment so shameful. But as you might understand, I have reclaimed a portion of my memories. Now, I may guard you better."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh. The light inside the bottle really does look more sprightly now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Yeah... It looks just like the lights I saw when Matriarch Babel was emerging from Azariq's tent."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...Let's change subjects."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Across the sands, there is still much of me that lies scattered. If you find it within yourself to offer me this generosity, my master, I will be beyond grateful should you collect my fragments and return me to wholeness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "In areas around a Jinni's fragments, a spot of green should flourish..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "This is because we Jinn always release energy around us to create an environment conducive to our slumber. I hope you shall bear this in mind."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I will."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "You have my thanks."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon will help too! Paimon's eyesight is second to none! Don't worry about it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Ah... I am invigorated! Come. Let us delve deeper."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Yeah. Let's go."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
