    "7318709": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Azariq",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "*huff* Let me see... Energy system, looks fine; engine, fine; weapons... the long-range sub-weapon is out of order, the main one isn't functioning normally; melee weapons and left arm, working..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Hmm, it all looks pretty good, to be honest!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, Jeht, what's wrong? You look like something's on your mind..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "N—No, it's nothing... It's just that I didn't get even half of what he said just now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Azariq feels like a different person. I've never seen him like this before..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "What? I've become more reliable, haven't I? Hahaha."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Autopilot... autopilot... Hmm, looks like it's been dismantled. Can't find that device at all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Sorry, it seems that we'll have to operate this big guy by ourselves."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You mean I have to, don't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Where are we heading?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Worry not, my master. I shall guide you from the side."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Oh, so you know the way?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Of course I do. I can sense the vibrations of my fragments, after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Well, guess we'll be troubling you to show us the way, then. Let's start this machine in the meantime, shall we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "On my way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Steady yourselves!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoaaa!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
