    "7318726": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Liloupar",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "As the shard of light merges with Liloupar's magic bottle, you feel a little of your own power being pulled away..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Through the Jinni's entranced eyes, you see a ravenous shepherd boy and a bright red pomegranate...\\nYou see the pomegranate juice flowing freely, like the wine of tyrants, the infatuation of lovers, and the fresh blood of innocent victims...\\nYou see the plump pomegranate being handed to the shepherd boy..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "\"Take a bite and use it to quench your thirst. But be careful not to let it burst in your hands...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, are you okay...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You suddenly froze up again, and you wouldn't respond to anyone... You really scared us there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "#Do not fret, {M#he}{F#she} is fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't worry, Jeht. I just zoned out for a bit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Phew, okay... Stop scaring us like that, though!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't worry, Paimon. I'll be fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh, fine, if you say so! Jeht was also really worried about you, you know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "My apologies if my troubled memories bothered you. But thanks to your help, my power has been restored... partly, in any case."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Pomegranates... Ah, pomegranates... The sweet fruit made from the congealed blood of the victimized... Should I have the chance to share it with you, my master, I surely will."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "How I desire to see the plump arils burst between your teeth, and how the rich juice overflows from your lips..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh... That does sound delicious, but Paimon doesn't think she's talking about fruit..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Ahem, we should go. There're still many mechanisms waiting for us ahead."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Now, now, little girl, are you sulking again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I'm not! I just said we should go!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Careful, the little wildcat is about to bite."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7318753": {
        "Desc": "Open the door",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, have you found anything?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Not yet! What about you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Have you found anything?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Not really... But I think we just need to move along the walls as we search."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About Azariq..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...What about him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Well... I know you may have doubts about him, but he's Matriarch Babel's most trusted subordinate, so it does us no good being suspicious all the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "That said, he does know a little too much, which makes me uneasy... But that's just a gut feeling, you know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Ah, but intuition can be quite accurate sometimes..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
