    "7318731": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Jeht and the others",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Alright... Now it looks like there's only one passage left for us to open."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What!? There's more!? Paimon's legs are already sore!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Oh? And you know this because you walk on your own two feet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Uh... Nah! Paimon was just, uh, speaking for {NICKNAME}! Yeah! Y—You must be tired, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Not really."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#Haha, {NICKNAME} is a veteran adventurer after all. You'd better exercise more, or {M#he'll}{F#she'll} leave you behind sooner or later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#N—No way! {NICKNAME} will definitely wait for Paimon, no matter what..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Ooh, I'm beat. Super beat."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#See? What did Paimon tell you? We've walked for so long that even {NICKNAME}'s tired!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#Hahaha! {M#He}{F#She} was just messing with you. This much walking is hardly a challenge for a veteran adventurer, you know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "But if you're really so tired, Paimon, why don't you let me carry you around? Hehehe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "N—No need! That would just be embarrassing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Hmm... My memory is gradually coming together. I can now guide you to the next location."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
