    "7310309": {
        "Desc": "Confront Azariq",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "What's wrong, Azariq? Feeling unwell? We can take a break if you're tired."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "No, I'm good. Real good, in fact."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Jeht, we need to talk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Hmm? Is it something important?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "#...Before that, {NICKNAME}, I have a favor to ask of you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Would you hand the Mother of the Jinn over into my keeping?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Well, well, aren't you a hasty lad? Far too hasty for your own good..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Azariq, you're like an elder brother to me, and I respect your guidance. But I... I don't understand. What's going on? Please, tell me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "I'm doing this for the Tanit. We're getting close to our destination, and it is for the best that we take care of the Mother of the Jinn, rather than leave her in an outsider's hands."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Is this... a request from Matriarch Babel?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "It is the rational choice. If she knew of this, she would give us her consent."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "That wasn't my question. I'm asking you, is this a request from Matriarch Babel!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "As I said, I do this for the Tanit. The Mother of the Jinn will be an invaluable asset in our hands, while in the hands of this outsider, she's nothing but a toy — a trinket."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Think about it! If we possess her power, we'll be able to recreate verdant oases in the desert again. Hasn't that been Matriarch Babel's pursuit this whole time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Once we finish this quest, Matriarch Babel will recognize your contributions by appointing you her successor, and your outlander friend will also be rewarded accordingly."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Everyone wins here. You, me... and of course, your friend."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "You'd agree with me too, wouldn't you, outlander?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I wouldn't be so sure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Liloupar doesn't seem to like you much. Paimon doubts she'd come with you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I respect Liloupar's decision."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, although, uh... she looks like a bottle right now, you should've asked for her consent first."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Hehe, well said. But allow me to remind you: the contract between my Master and I can only be broken by death."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "You are right. My apologies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "This is nonsense..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I said that this is nonsense, and you're full of it... traitor."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You insult me with your filthy lies, and I demand the right to respond with my blades."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Whoa... Just a second there, little wildcat. We were just having a friendly conversation. Why did you suddenly go berserk? Haven't we always been like family to each other?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Family? Perhaps... and perhaps not."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "First, you plot murder against our guests and taint our hospitality without Matriarch Babel's permission. This is an act of betrayal."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Second, you've learned technologies from the northerners, but you've refused to share the knowledge with the tribe. That is against our code."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "And third, you deceive your fellow tribes-people and place them in peril."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You're right, you know. I've always tried to view you as my brother. But what about you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You have forgotten your mother's name. Thus, I demand that you cleanse your defilement with your weapons."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Wait. Calm down, calm down. Look, we're in the middle of the desert. If you kill me now, who will be able to prove your innocence?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "\"Oh? So our little wildcat has finally bared her fangs against her tribe, huh?\" That's what everyone will say. You'll be seen as a traitor."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Will someone who has betrayed their own tribe ever be accepted in the desert again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "So what? The only reason I've let you live till now is that you never did us any harm. But now, that reason, too, is gone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "I suggest you calm yourself down. We can still talk. There's no need to resort to violence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I am calm! Pick up your blade!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "*sigh* I didn't expect things would go this far... I can only hope you will forgive me."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
