    "7310311": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Azariq",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "*gasp* Wait, please, stop, little wildcat..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Shut up. You disgust me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "*gasp* I'm not asking for your forgiveness. Just... hear me out..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Last words, huh? Make it quick."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "You... you let me down... Jeht, I thought you'd understand... *gasp* I reckoned we could work together..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "*gasp* You... struggled outside to make a living, too... We are so alike... You care about the Tanit... and you've always been loyal, no?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Please reconsider... *gasp* Think about it... Imagine what the Eternal Oasis will bring us... An infinite future, fertile fields, and endless opportunities..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Future children... will no longer have to beg for food from that city in the rainforest, nor will they need to learn the killer's trade. They will no longer have to rely on some strongman just to live with some dignity..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Think about it, Jeht... Babel is... no worthier... than us... to rule the Tanit..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "*gasp* Think, Jeht, think... You're a smart girl... You would... have done the same... for the Tanit..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Are you finished?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Go... If you... spare my life... I can get my friends on the outside to... spare yours, too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azariq",
                    "T": "Ha... Or what? Are you... *gasp* willing to be the first member of our tribe who... slaughters your own? I hope you have given thought to... the fate of traitors—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "\"The one who fails to return alive is the traitor... or so you just told me.\"\\nSays Jeht."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Are you alright, Jeht?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "No. I... want to throw up, actually."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Ahem. I understand if you may wish to mourn for your fellow tribesman or something... But I am obliged to tell you that this big thing will not hold up for much longer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "My master, for your own safety, we should leave as soon as possible."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Yes... Let's go."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
