    "7310318": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Jeht",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Hmph... I need to wipe my blades. Help me keep watch."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He was working with Azariq..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Judge the criminal first, then find the evidence, huh... Whatever. It makes no difference."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why do villains always leave a trail to be found..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Beats Paimon... Hey, that's not the point!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Azariq... So he wanted to murder Matriarch Babel, then become the co-leader of the Tanit with me by \"marriage\"... and then make us all puppets for the northerners?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...And that's why he had to take you, who might already know what was going on, out of the picture, and gain control over the Jinni. From the very beginning, he had assumed that I would trust him absolutely and go along with his scheme..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I trusted him so much, too! I never... I never imagined he was such a disgusting person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Alright. Revenge has been had, and the drama comes to a close. Drumroll please! And who has had the last laugh? Oh my, it's our little Jeht!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "*sigh* This is exhausting. Shall we proceed?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Matriarch Babel needs to know about this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Returning now just to give her a report? Oh, I wouldn't call that wisdom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Do you really think that desert woman would believe that these two stupid men — and not you — are the traitors if you return empty-handed?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "For the sake of argument, let's assume you have proof of their betrayal. But knowing what you do of the desert dwellers' traditions, do you think your tribe will focus on the evidence and not pay a single slice of attention to the fact that you killed your tribesmen?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Will Matriarch Babel have eyes only for the proof and forgive the shame caused by your brutal slaughter? I, for one, think she'd much rather hear some good news."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "If you wish to return to rest for a moment, you can. But speak nothing of what transpired here. That is my advice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Agreed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... You two didn't argue at all. That sure is a new one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Liloupar's analysis is on point."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're growing wiser, Jeht."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "If we didn't have more important things to do, I would've cut their heads off and taken them back with me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well then, let's move on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Alright. I will watch your back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Speaking of which, where are we going?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The big iron ball is totally broken, and there are no clear paths around."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Worry not, little one, you still have me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Well, there is this hole over there that the big iron ball created as it fell. We should be able to reach our destination if we go through it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? So you can sense stuff like that too? Wow, you're better than a compass! Maybe Paimon should call you Liloupass from now on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "As I said, my fragment guides me. Let us go. Enter that big iron ball, and we should find a path from there."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
