    "7310320": {
        "Desc": "Proceed deeper",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "So... are we just one last step away from reaching the Eternal Oasis now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's the matter? Are you unhappy, Jeht?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Are you alright?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Hmm... I don't know. I mean, I do look forward to fulfilling my parents' dreams at last."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "But I can't help but get mixed feelings when I think of all that we've been through along the way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Although I now have the tribe to call home, betrayals and schemes are never far from me. Are the Tanit truly where I belong? Have I really been accepted by them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What's wrong? You seem preoccupied."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Haha, I'm alright. I'm in a good mood, actually. It's just... *sigh*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Dad went through all kinds of setbacks and betrayals in his adventures, and I just realized that I'm on the same unfortunate path as him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Although I now have the tribe to call home, betrayals and schemes are never far from me. Are the Tanit truly where I belong? Have I really been accepted by them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Jeht..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Umm... Let's not wallow in the sad things, Jeht. The past is the past... and anyway, we've beaten all the bad guys now, haven't we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon's right. It's water under the bridge now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Yeah, you're right. Let them sink into the sands. We have more important things to do!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "But... *sigh* When Dad was with me, I could say \"Home is where Dad is.\" But now, I'm all alone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's not the end of the world even if that isn't where you truly belong."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Ha, you're so carefree! You know, I was starting to forget that you're a traveler, unconstrained anywhere by anything or anyone!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "It's only that... hehe... when Dad was with me, I could say \"Home is where Dad is.\" But now, I'm all by myself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Gah, stop wallowing in self-pity, Jeht. You're better than this! Also, we're here for you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "*chuckle* Don't get mad, Paimon. But you're right. I need to keep my chin up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Now we're talking! Huh. Aren't we supposed to head out now? We can go up using this platform, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Haha, alright! Now, enough sentimentality. Let's go!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
