    "7310323": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Liloupar",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "As the shard of light merges with Liloupar's magic bottle, you feel a little of your own power being pulled away..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Through the Jinni's entranced eyes, you see flaring flames and blunt blades...\\nYou see the freezing moonlight and viscous honey...\\nThrough the golden honey, you see the underlying scheme..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "The princess sees the consequences of her innocuous error, her sanity giving way to madness...\\nHer invincible husband is shaken by the tragedy, his greedy heart blinded by ecstasy...\\nAll the sorrow, joy, and madness are finally turned into food for the Jinn-Mother to devour..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "\"It is curtains for the carnivorous Night of Honey — Such is the end of the Jinni's lover...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#{M#Listen here, Jinni. If anything happens to him, I'll get you for that.}{F#Listen here, Jinni. If this does any harm to her, I'll get you for that.}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Harm? Oh, come now. Addiction, though... Now that is a more probable risk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Addiction is not okay, either! It's unacceptable no matter what!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "The golden honey, the golden scheme... Departure breaks the heart, yet the kingdom lives on under the usurper's rule..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are you saying?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "You have seen that which I speak of."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You... It was you who murdered them..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "It was not \"murder\"... It was punishment. For my lover, and for myself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "I once believed that he would bring this land into a bright future, but he proved no different from the other shallow, mortal tyrants. I was furious... No, I was in pain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "I was once deeply and madly in love with him, but when I was betrayed like that... Only destruction three times greater than that love could quell my sorrow and pain... Perhaps."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "In short... I used the hands and hearts of my own children to complete an impeccable killing. Such is the consequence of betrayal."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Let's get moving. This is giving me goosebumps."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
