    "7310333": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Ferigees",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ahh! What is this place?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "C—Careful! I sense a strange power!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "...You. The destroyer of Gurabad, the Mother of the Despicable."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "I have returned, sister."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "\"Sister\"? I don't understand. Are you calling me... \"sister\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Yes. Ferigees, my sister... I have returned."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "#You are here to see our mistress, aren't you? Let me guess, you have brought your new master and... {M#his}{F#her} desert slave?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "This person's starting to tick me off..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, sure sounds like she's Liloupar's sister, alright."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It seems to run in the family..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow... If that's the case, Paimon certainly doesn't want to be a guest at their place..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "Hmph. You cannot pass."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Ferigees, I understand your concerns. I would even be willing to bow in apology, but please, let me see our slumbering mistress, if for but a moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "You are worthy no longer, fallen traitor. There is no place for you now in the oasis realm."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "Leave now, before my patience runs dry and these mechanical shackles rumble, and never show yourselves here again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "Sister, you shed the form of a Jinni and constrained yourself to this husk for thousands of years. Is this the \"survival\" that you so desired to pursue?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "So, you dispense your kindness to me? Despicable traitor, my shackles have nothing to do with you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "Ugh... Agh... Ahh...! The shackles... they tighten... Leave! Leave now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Liloupar",
                    "T": "My master, if I may so ask, please assist me in freeing my sister from her suffering..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Hold on, I don't get it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You mean..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferigees",
                    "T": "Still so arrogant and inconstant... You disappoint me, my sister."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Gah! Paimon hasn't even figured out what's going on yet, and we're about to fight already!?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
